{"id":345997,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/05/沈浩波：请放了119名衣衫单薄-瑟瑟发抖的姐妹/","date":"2014-05-11T02:05:56Z","modified":"2014-05-12T05:30:32Z","title":"沈浩波：请放了119名衣衫单薄 瑟瑟发抖的姐妹","content":"<div id=\"postmessage_19061816\" style=\"color: #2b2b2b;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">凤凰网报道：</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2009</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">25</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">日</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">晚</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">时</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">15</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分，西安警方</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">20</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">多辆警车，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">50</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">多名民警突袭某夜总会，将</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名陪侍女用三辆公交车带走。还配有图画。是历年抓捕人数最多云云。。。。。。</span></div>\n<div style=\"color: #2b2b2b;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这样的新闻很多，年年有表现。看罢无语。继而悲伤，继而愤怒，继而又是深深的悲凉。继而写下“相煎何急”！继而写下这首诗。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">                                        </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">——题记</span>今夜，我在北中国的一个村庄发呆<br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在这个深秋渐凉的夜晚被带走了</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">塞进三辆公交汽车中</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">带走了</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">她们是陪侍女</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">灯红酒绿中的边缘人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是一群女人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">被</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">50</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">多名全副武装的人民的警察</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">带走了</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">她们是正统道德不齿的一群人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">她们是游走在各个城市给孤独的男人们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">带去慰籍的一群人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一群年轻的女人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在商品社会中</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在公平的交易中</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">被带走了</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">凄婉的笑</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">哀怨的眼</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">沉重的魂</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在一次次虚伪的扫荡中</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">跌落红尘</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">碎了</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以诗人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小者的声音</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我请求</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请求你们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">放了</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请原谅她们的堕落</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">就象原谅我们自己</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">抬起头</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">仰望漆黑的夜空</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那冷得发抖</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">挤成一团的星星啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">能否仅凭自己</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在无涯的荒漠</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">找到温暖的阳光</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以诗人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小者的声音</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我请求</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请求你们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">放了</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">她们的身后</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">是</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个家庭</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个家庭中的成员</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要靠她们赚来的金钱卑微的</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">活在尘嚣置上的大地</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卑微的生长</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卑微的死去</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亲爱的爸爸</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亲爱的妈妈</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亲爱的姐姐</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亲爱的妹妹</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亲爱的哥哥</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">亲爱的弟弟</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">还有万里山河阳光照不到的遗忘的角落</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不能因为我们卑微</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">就没有活着的尊严</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">还有这高楼</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这大厦</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这现代化滋养的</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">广袤土地的一切</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以诗人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小者的声音</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我请求</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请求你们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">放了</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请把我们有限的警力投入西北边陲</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那里狼烟正起</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">浊流暗涌</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">热比娅之流们还在逍遥</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请把尊严还给我们的警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（一次次这样的行动中</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">他们尊严扫地）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让他们在真正的黑暗中施展拳脚</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">保护卑微的弱小者</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请不要让这些纠纠雄姿</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对着</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以诗人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小者的声音</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我请求</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请求你们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">放了</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹吧</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让我们把更大的力量</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更远的目光投向东方</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那里</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">小小的钓鱼岛正孤军奋战</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让我们把更大的力量</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更远的目光投向南方</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那广袤无垠的南中国海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">母亲的肢体正被肆无忌惮的瓜分</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让我们把更大的力量</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更远的目光投向印度洋</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">“德新海”在无助的呻吟</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">25</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">个海员兄弟正日夜煎熬</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">望眼欲穿</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让我们把更大的力量</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">更远的目光投向这片土地</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">消灭贫穷</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">而不是制造贫穷</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以诗人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小者的声音</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我请求</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请求你们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">放了</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">或者</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">只要愿意</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">你们至少也应该</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让几个男人陪着她们上路</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">哪怕只有一个</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（画面中一个也没有）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公交车很拥挤</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">心灵很寂寞</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以诗人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小者的声音</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我请求</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请求你们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">放了</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请得到了卑微者慰籍的尊贵者们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这些道貌岸然</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">衣冠楚楚</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">无限强大的各界精英</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这些内心胆怯</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">灵魂没有归宿</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">时时惊恐不安的宵小之辈</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请勇敢的站出来吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这巨大的不公和欺辱</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">不要让姐妹们弱小的肩头独自承担</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请和她们站在一起</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请微笑</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请剥掉所有的面具吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">哪怕泪水</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">哪怕屈辱</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">哪怕从此苦海无边</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">仅仅做为一个男人和她们站在一起</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">就以这样的方式证明吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在最后的审判到来之前</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">告诉这个夜晚的天空</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">——千百年来深邃的主宰</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那堕入地狱的灵魂是可以救赎的</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这才是伟大的本质啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这才是大爱无边</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">连上帝也会恸哭</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">他分明是看到了自己</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">他就是在恸哭自己啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">这一个个瞬间灵魂已经和上帝在一起的男人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以这样的方式</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">站立着</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">赎了自己的罪</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以诗人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小者的声音</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我祈祷</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让我看到这一幕吧</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我将依旧相信</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在钢筋水泥的冰冷中</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">血还是热的</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我将依旧相信</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">无数的暴风雨后</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">天空还是蔚蓝</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我将依旧相信</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那些美丽的童话还在我们每晚的梦中</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我将依旧相信</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在不远的将来</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一个了不起的民族将真正崛起</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在它长久孤独的奋斗中</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我看到幸福将在这片土地生根</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以诗人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小者的声音</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我请求</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请求你们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">放了</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">把爱和宽容留给她们吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">让我们只握住一颗泪珠</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">泪珠里映照着我们各自的脸庞</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">真实而又清晰</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">渺小而又伟大</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">以诗人</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小者的声音</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我请求</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">  </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请求你们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">放了</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">119</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">名衣衫单薄</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瑟瑟发抖的姐妹</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请让她们回家</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">请让人民的警察们也回家吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那些围观者</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那些看客们</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那些媒体</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那些阵地</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那些强大无比的关怀</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">那些嘲笑怜悯</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">都回家吧</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也让我</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">当今最弱小的诗人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">回家吧</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">虽然</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">在这样的夜晚</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我们都已</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">      </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">无家可归</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"> </span></p>\n","author":999,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016,9203],"tags":[8641,25095]}